{"tid":1240792,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"每個禮拜日遊行都係一種佔領，對商家佬嘅damage","createTime":"2019-06-18T12:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T14:24:32.000Z","uid":185824,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"73b0cfe4e4b947188f6713f2fe739dea0ac969b9","tid":1240792,"uid":185824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"同朋友諗計，<br />\n其實遊行唔係冇用架，<br />\n不過可能理解錯左以為遊行係齋行，<br />\n其實遊行係會令到遊行路線附近既交通癱喚，生意會有影響。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希慎同sogo冇曬生意</span></strong></span>，生意佬會唔會好似麥美娟咁屌死林鄭，你影響我利益啊！！！<br />\n建議民陣將條路線有咁長拉咁長，終點唔一定要政總，轉吓中聯辦，轉吓禮賓府咁。<br />\n大家唔一定要行晒，<br />\n行到累就坐底，啲商場出入口有樓梯可以休息涼冷氣。我地唔係有屈學生嘅食肆list咩？去涼吓冷氣、唱吓聖詩、開吓唸佛經機。<br />\n- 大家唔洗咁累<br />\n- 1/7 時間港島北全癱<br />\n- 升級既話轉做閒日威力更大（過左612之後好似比較難）<br />\n<br />\nPS 連每個星期同佢攬炒半日都話累，話不了，腳支持唔住果啲，調轉頭話和非理對唔住義士，我笑左。你肯定自己係行動者？<br />\n法國每年有幾多大大小小遊行都係靠積累出來，"},{"pid":"10d6a0fbc56311422ae8545bbeb8fa8715316782","tid":1240792,"uid":185824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9563bd3c6191c2ec4ca1f14efd70da4b9c5c4d5","tid":1240792,"uid":185824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2018ebcbf8abee72f654abb254754a145036db9c","tid":1240792,"uid":185824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aadd7834248b55e98f3864d0b7e3f6fc81c8974","tid":1240792,"uid":185824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:24:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3bd453d2efee60ed50ce7051c04d8fc51d1c498f","tid":1240792,"uid":185824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8feed6c8c4700e0bef9aeffeb142ef792d8bb4d","tid":1240792,"uid":185824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0